583
00:34:17,655 --> 00:34:20,240
- Somewhere around 1000 kilos.
- [Gustavo] 1000 kilos?

584
00:34:20,324 --> 00:34:22,076
Counting the gasoline.

585
00:34:30,877 --> 00:34:32,003
Carlos...

586
00:34:32,879 --> 00:34:34,005
