695
00:42:00,742 --> 00:42:02,536
We tried to save the baby...

696
00:42:08,041 --> 00:42:10,085
The baby died in my hands.

697
00:42:12,838 --> 00:42:14,340
I'm so sorry.

698
00:42:15,090 --> 00:42:18,093
